r>6.        The sponsor shall arrange groupings with at least three other guild members a minimum of three times each.<br>7.        Once the groupings have been completed, the sponsor will submit the persons name to the correct class officer.<br>8.        The class officer will speak with the members who have grouped with the person, and review any comments posted on the message board.<br>9.        Provided that there is nothing unfavorable revealed about the person through this process, the class officer can make arrangements to issue a guild invite to the person.<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub88.ezboard.com/ussnaake.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ssnaake</A> at: 2/19/02 5:29:19 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=163.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm10.showNextMessage?topicID=163.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=163.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm10.emailToFriend?topicID=163.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm10.threadControl?topicID=163.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=163.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroe